Hi Team,
Does this feature *`Select prebuilt classes to add`* pull fields from published apps schema ?
Actually we have published the Passport App with additional fields but they are not reflecting here.

cc : @Nithin @Anshu

@Prasad not all the published apps in the Marketplace are part of this pre-built class option. This is the reason you are not able to see the updated schema of the Passport app here. cc @Kaustubh (KD)

@Prasad This is a gap right now that we are going to partially address with https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-2387 cc: @jack.robbins. The longer vision is that this gets populated by the the Marketplace
